pan style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">1. 100mM NH<sub>4</sub>HCO<sub>3</sub></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">：称取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">1.581 g NH<sub>4</sub>HCO<sub>3</sub>(MW 79.06)</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">溶于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">200 ml </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">超纯水中（有效期：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">2</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">个月）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\"> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">2.<span style=\"mso-spacerun:yes;\">&nbsp; </span>25 mM NH<sub>4</sub>HCO<sub>3</sub></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">：称取</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">0.396 g NH<sub>4</sub>HCO<sub>3</sub></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">溶于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">200 ml </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">超纯水中（有效期：</sp