-family:&quot;\">（有效期：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">6</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">个月）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">5. 60% ACN/0.1%\r\nTFA</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">39.9ml </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">超纯水中加入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">60ml100%ACN</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">0.1mlTFA</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">（有效期：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">3</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">个月）</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:small;\"> </span> \r\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;\">\r\n\t<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">6. TPCK-Trypsin</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">无需配制，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;\">Promega</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;\">公司已提供成品，